title: Voyage to the Bottom of the Sea S04E17 Nightmare
description:
Voyage to the Bottom of the Sea

S04E17
Nightmare

One of 26 episodes from Season Four which are not yet on DVD
Remastered audio and video from VHS

Includes preview of next week's episode, "The Abominable Snowman"

Airdate: January 28, 1968

Summoned to the Seaview, Crane (David Hedison) is confronted with a mysterious force field---and the voices of the missing crew.

Nelson: Richard Basehart. Bentley: Paul Mantee. Morton: Bob Dowdell. Patterson: Paul Trinka. Kowalski: Del Monroe
